\v 27 Kodwa wena, ungesabi,\x + 30.10,11; 46.27,28.\x* nceku yami Jakobe, ungatshaywa luvalo, Israyeli, ngoba khangela, ngizakusindisa usekhatshana, lenzalo yakho elizweni lokuthunjwa kwayo; uJakobe uzaphenduka-ke, athule, onwabe, njalo kakho oza\add m\add*ethusa.
